#: ../../../_spack_root/lib/spack/spack/environment/__init__.py:docstring of
#: spack.environment:8
msgid ""
"Spack environments have existed since Spack ``v0.12.0``, and there have been "
"4 different ``spack.lock`` formats since then. The formats are documented "
"here."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../_spack_root/lib/spack/spack/environment/__init__.py:docstring of
#: spack.environment:11
msgid ""
"The high-level format of a Spack lockfile hasn't changed much between "
"versions, but the contents have.  Lockfiles are JSON-formatted and their top-"
"level sections are:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../_spack_root/lib/spack/spack/environment/__init__.py:docstring of
#: spack.environment:14
msgid ""
"``_meta`` (object): this contains details about the file format, including:"
msgstr ""

